<br />By creating an account on one of the Games, you automatically access to the services provided with the Community Platform. These services are free and without obligation of purchase.<br />The Community Platform enables you to play any of the Games with the same account. On this account your statistics, friend list and tribe are saved. You can use this account to chat with your friends and tribe members while playing another game of the community platform. You can also access the Forums via the Games.<br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#009D9D;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.3 Forum</span></span></span><br />By creating an account on of the Games, you can then access to the Forums. The Forums are available via the Games and at <a href="http://<?=$ayarlar['title']?>.com/forums" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">http://<?=$ayarlar['title']?>.com/forums</a>. Access and participation in the Forums are free and without obligation of purchase.<br />You agree that <?=$ayarlar['title']?> SARL cannot guarantee access to the Forums as the society is not responsible for any hardware, software or Internet access, quality, suitability or unavailability issues. <br />If you do not respect these Terms and Conditions of Use, your account will be banned from the Forums.<br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#009D9D;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.4 Purchasing procedure</span></span></span><br /><?=$ayarlar['title']?> enables you to purchase items to customize your character. You can purchase these items for free by using the in game money - “Cheese” in <?=$ayarlar['title']?>, “Hazelnut” in Bouboum, &quot;Potatoes&quot; in Fortoresse.<br /><br /><span style="color:#30BA76;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.4.1 Credits: “Fraise”</span></span><br />Some items can also be purchased by buying credits - “Fraise”. For the time being, this option is only available in the game <?=$ayarlar['title']?>.<br />Please note that character customization is only available to registered users.<br />Only registered users that have linked an email address to their account can purchase Fraises.<br />If you are under the age of 18, you must have your parents or guardian agreement to purchase Fraise on the Games. In any case, even if you are over the age of 18, you must be the owner of the means of payment used to purchase Fraise (credit card, bank account, phone, money etc.).<br />You understand and agree that we are relying upon that representation in allowing you to use the Service.<br />Means of payment depends of countries and services used. <?=$ayarlar['title']?> SARL is not liable for the lack of a mean of payment for a specific country. <br /><br /><span style="color:#30BA76;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.4.2 Fraise purchasing procedure</span></span><br />To purchase Fraise, please follow this procedure:<br />1. Log in the game.<br />2. Open the shop.<br />3. Choose “Buy Fraises”.<br />If you did not link an email address to your account, a window to validate an email address will open.<br />4. Choose the amount of Fraises.<br />5. Choose the purchase platform (Zong or Paypal).<br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Purchase with Paypal:</span><br />a. Check your order on Paypal.<br />b. Log in Paypal.<br />c. Validate your order on Paypal.<br />d. Go back to the game.<br />e. Validate your order in game.<br />Only when you have validated your order in game, your bank account will be debited.  Fraises will be immediately credited on your in game account.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Purchase with Zong:</span><br />a. Type in your phone number.<br />b. You will receive a text message. Depending depending on your country of residence, you will be asked to either type in a 4 digit PIN (provided in the text message) or reply to the text message to confirm the payment.<br />Fraises will be credited on your account when you have finish Zong procedure.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Purchase with Allopass:</span><br />Depending on your country of residence, available payment methods may vary. (Cf. 5.2.5 Allopass) <br />a. Select your payment method.<br />b. Follow the follow the guidelines to obtain your Allopass access code.<br /><br /><span style="color:#30BA76;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.4.3 Paypal</span></span><br />Paypal is an international payment platform.<br />Paypal is used to pay by card or bank transfer. Registration is not required to pay by card. Registering enables to pay with other ways (bank transfer) and to save your choices for ulterior purchase.<br />Paypal guarantees the security of payments and confidentiality of the personal data.<br /><br />Atelier  801 SARL is not liable for any problem occurring with Paypal . <br />Customer support is available at : <a href="https://www.paypal.com/fr/cgi-bin/helpweb?cmd=_help" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">Help Paypal</a> .<br /><br /><span style="color:#30BA76;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.4.4 Zong</span></span><br />Zong is an international payment platform.<br />Zong is used to pay by text messages. Registration is not required to use Zong services. <br />Zong guarantees the security of payments and confidentiality of the personal data.<br /><br />Atelier  801 SARL is not liable for any problem occurring with Zong. <br />Customer support is available at : <a href="http://www.zong.com/help" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">Help Zong</a> .<br /><br /><span style="color:#30BA76;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.4.5 Allopass</span></span><br />Allopass is an international payment platform.<br />Allopass is a safe and easy payment service that enables you to buy online content without having to expose your credit card or banking information to any third party, including Allopass. Instead, you can pay for online content using phone payment, SMS payment, prepaid cards, Internet + (Internet Service Provider direct debit), Neosurf (prepaid card) available in the Neosurf points of sales in France, Spain, Andorra, Belgium, Switzerland, Algeria, Cameroon, Congo, Ivory Coast, Morocco and Senegal), electronic wallet.<br />Registration is not required to use Allopass services.<br /><br /><span style="color:#92CF91;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">Mobile Payment : SMS, Internet+ Mobile, Mikro Odeme</span></span><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">SMS -</span> To buy an Allopass code, web users click on their country&#39;s flag and send a text-message to the short number displayed on the screen. In return users will receive a SMS with a code to be inputted on the website in order to access paid content/service. Web users are directly billed by the telecom provider. The merchant&#39;s Allopass account is credited in real time for each valid code inputted in the site. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/sms" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Internet+ Mobile -</span> Internet+ Mobile is a french mobile phone billing solution. It allows to charge in a few clicks (one off purchase or subscription) via mobile operators’ bill, multimedia services and contents from mobile internet, web and mobile applications. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/wapplus" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Mikro Odeme - </span>Mikro-Odeme allows you to pay online via mobile phone, without the need of a credit card or via wire transfer. The web user enters their mobile phone number and their telecom operator bills them directly. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/turkcell" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="color:#92CF91;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">IVR (Payment by Phone) : Home Phone Billing</span></span><br />Web users click on their country&#39;s flag and dial the number displayed on the screen. Users will hear a pre-recorded message of a code that they must input on to the website in order to access the paid content/service. Web users are billed directly by the telecom provider. The merchant&#39;s Allopass account is credited in real time for each valid code inputted on the site. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/audiotel" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="color:#92CF91;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">ISP Billing : Internet+</span></span><br />Internet+ is a secure payment solution. The online purchase amount of internet subscribers is directly taken from the internet bill (30€ maximum per transaction). <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/wha" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="color:#92CF91;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">Prepaid Card : Neosurf, Paysafecard, Zeevex</span></span><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Neosurf - </span>Neosurf is a prepaid card available at Neosurf points of sale outlets that allows you to buy easily and safely on the internet. To make online purchase, web users enter the code on the back of the card, onto the website. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/neosurf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Paysafecard -</span> Paysafecard is a pre-paid payment solution available in more than 3.500 points of sale in France and abroad. Paysafecard helps you completing various online digital content purchases from the entertainment industry. Buyer will exchange cash for paysafecard at a local sales outlet. Then he will receive a Paysafecard 16-digit PIN for those following amounts, 10, 25, 50 or 100€. This PIN will help completing its transactions for plenty of different digital content. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/paysafecard" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Zeevex - </span>Zeevex is a virtual currency originally designed for gamers. Zeevex works for any amount from $5 to $100. The digital units, Zeevex tokens, are sold as a prepaid card worth $5, $10 and $20 . This cards are available in 40 000 points of sale outlets across the US. Web users buy a Zeevex card and activate it via iphone or the web. The Zeevex tokens obtained can be immediately used for online purchases of games or other digital contents. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/zeevex" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="color:#92CF91;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">E-wallet : Hipay, Dineromail</span></span><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Hipay -</span> Hipay is a multi-currency e-wallet that allows you amongst other things, to make online transactions easily and safely, to transfer money to other users and also to manage your children’s pocket money. In effect, each user can create subaccounts from their master Hipay account for other members of their family. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/hipay" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Dineromail -</span> Dineromail is an e-wallet that allows you to make online transactions in Latin America. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/dineromail-wallet" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="color:#92CF91;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">Cash Payment : Dineromail, Payshop</span></span><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Dineromail -</span> Web users enter the amount they want to be credited on their account. They receive an invoice which needs to be printed out and go to the nearest outlet to pay. The money is credited on their Dineromail account. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/dineromail-cash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight:bold;">Payshop -</span> Payshop is a payment solution that allows Internet users to pay for online purchases by visiting a Payshop agent (outlets such as newsagents, petrol stations, supermarkets, etc...) equipped with an invoice or a reference. <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/products-services/payshop" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">More information</a><br /><br />Atelier  801 SARL is not liable for any problem occurring with Allopass . <br />Customer support is available at : <a href="http://www.allopass.com/uk/support/faq/buyer" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">Help Allopass</a><br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#009D9D;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">5.5 Referrals</span></span></span><br />The Games offers you the possibility to refer new players. To do so, referees have to create a new account via the link given in the menu “More [in game money]”. Each referred player enables his referrer to win 1 in game free credit (Cheese in <?=$ayarlar['title']?>, Hazelnut in Bouboum, Potato in Fortoresse) every 10 free in game credits collected by the referred player.<br /><?=$ayarlar['title']?> assumes no liability if the link is posted on a third-party website in violation with the rules of aforesaid website. <?=$ayarlar['title']?> SARL does not offer any purchasable credits (Fraises) for the use and distribution of the referral link. <?=$ayarlar['title']?> SARL does not offer any free credits to referred players. <?=$ayarlar['title']?> SARL assumes no liability if the link is posted with a false promise of free credits and/or purchasable credits. If you encounter such acts, you can report them via the <a href="<?=$site?>/contact" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return verifierLienMemePageMessage(event);">contact form</a> .<br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#98E2EB;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">6. Privacy</span></span></span><br /><br />Please review our Privacy Policy, for information regarding the collection, use and distribution of personal information collected through this Website, which is published on the Website, currently at “Privacy Policy”<br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#98E2EB;"><span style="font-weight:bold;">7. Games Updates</span></span></span><br /><br />Update or “patch” are made directly on servers and do not have any consequences on your computer.
